            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20221116-1333689</guid>
            <link>https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20221116-1333689</link>
            
            
            
            
            
                
            
            
        </item>
        
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[中国新增冠病病例破两万]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>中国大陆星期二（</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>11月15日）新增20059起本土冠病感染者，过去几天的病例数量整体呈上升趋势，病例主要分布在广东、北京、重庆、河南、内蒙古等地。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据中国国家卫生健康委员会通报，中国大陆</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>1568</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>18491</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>北京</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>197</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>174</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者，相比之下，14日有</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>303</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>59名无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>北京朝阳区星期一（</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>11月</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>14日）关闭大量公共区域核酸检测点后，出现大排长龙的核酸检测队伍。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>北京市政府新闻发言人徐和建15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>表示，涉疫重点地区核酸检测点位通道将只增不减，以保持检测力度。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>广东15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>564</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>6215</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>广东省在当天发布关于优化调整隔离管理措施的紧急通知，要求密切接触者和入境人员管理措施调整为“5天集中隔离+3天居家隔离”，期间不得外出；高风险区外溢人员进行“7天居家隔离”；高风险岗位人员进行“5天居家健康监测”。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>重庆15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>126</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>2688</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>重庆市委书记陈敏尔在当日召开的重庆市新冠肺炎</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>疫情防控工作电视电话会议上说，要确保管控区坚决围住捞干，力争社会面尽快遏制、下降、清零。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>河南15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>200</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>1674</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者，其中郑州占多数病例，有200</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>确诊病例和1650名无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<div id="innity-in-post"></div>
<div id="dfp-ad-midarticlespecial">
        
</div>



<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>另外，内蒙古15</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>日新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>82</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>1194</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者；</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>甘肃</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>新增</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>13</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>起本土确诊病例和</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>2688</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


